{
  "stem": "27687.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were secretaries sitting there, and they were marking down my name and how tall and this and that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I went around this way into another room, and I had different clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they looked my size, and they gave me good clothes, and gave me nice shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And right from there, we went to another barrack, and they said in about two hours, we give-- we give you to eat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the buses will be here, and you will go to the station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oh, fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they brought us food-- good food-- and cake and chocolate and fruits and everything and so-- and then we went into the buses, and then they took us out from the station.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we drove to Northern France, to Brest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the way, they were so good to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every time we came to a station, they came to the windows, and they asked if we wanted something to drink, if we wanted something to eat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every station, and finally we came down to Brest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to Brest, and we looked around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all we saw was bunkers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bunkers and bunkers and bunkers and bunkers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we figured, what are we going to do here, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, so they brought us to the camp, and they gave us to eat again, and everybody had a bed, and it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We only were about four people in a room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next day, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what it was is they were building bunkers for U-boats-- underwater ships, the U-boats.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all they were doing is pouring cement, lots of cement-- cement, cement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every day the trains came in with lots of cement.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
